message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (computational linguistics) as audio tagging involves natural language processing, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a deep learning-based approach, cs.CV (computer vision) as the auxiliary CNN is designed to learn on the spatial features of stereo recordings, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with audio data.
